DisplayField.SubQuery: SELECT DISTINCT COALESCE(label,sharing_share_xnat_experimentda_id) AS ashsdata_project_id,sharing_share_xnat_experimentda_id FROM ( SELECT sharing_share_xnat_experimentda_id,label FROM xnat_experimentdata_share WHERE project='@WHERE' UNION SELECT id,label FROM xnat_experimentData WHERE project='@WHERE' )SEARCH

SELECT DISTINCT ON ( e.ID) e.ID AS expt_id,field FROM xnat_experimentData_field ef JOIN (SELECT ID,extension,element_name FROM xnat_experimentData e JOIN xdat_meta_element xme ON e.extension=xme.xdat_meta_element_id WHERE xme.element_name='ashs:ashsData') e on ef.fields_field_xnat_experimentdat_id=e.id WHERE name='@WHERE'
